Starry, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:25 PM ET
Communications Equipment

Company Overview of Starry, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Starry, Inc. develops Wi-Fi touch screen routers. The company’s product features include the ability proactively identify issues with Internet performance and suggests ways to fix them through notifications surfaced through its touchscreen. Its product is available for sale on Starry.com and pre-order on Amazon launchpad. The company was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts with an operation in New York, New York.


38 Chauncy Street2nd FloorBoston, MA 02111United StatesFounded in 2014



Phone: 617-861-8300

